node.text:
For me, hockey is more than just a sport. It’s a lifestyle. 
From endless hours on the pond to 3am chel sessions, there are so many ways to play the game that we love. I’m pumped to announce that I’ll be joining the @BauerHockey team as an Official Bauer Athlete in growing our beautiful game together. This is just the beginning.
